title._content: Prinses Juliana en Eleanor Roosevelt / Princess Juliana and Eleanor Roosevelt

description._content: Spaarnestad Photo, SFA002006659 Eleanor Roosevelt en kroonprinses Juliana in de Ridderzaal in Den Haag, waar de Amerikaanse presidentsweduwe wordt gehuldigd, Nederland 19 april 1948. Collectie SPAARNESTAD PHOTO/Henk Blansjaar Eleanor Roosevelt and the Dutch crown princess Juliana in Knights' Hall in The Hague where the widow of the American president is honoured. The Netherlands, 19 April 1948.
